{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":359726,"duration_api_ms":308263,"num_turns":39,"result":"Implementation complete. All changes are in `lib/agent.sh` only. Here's what was done:\n\n**Milestone 0.5: Agent Output Monitoring And Null-Run Detection**\n\nThe core problem: `--output-format json` produces no streaming FIFO output, causing the activity timeout to kill healthy agents and the null-run heuristic to discard completed work.\n\n**Solution — three complementary signals:**\n\n1. **FIFO activity timeout now checks for file changes** before killing. When the read loop times out, it runs `find -newer` against a timestamp marker. If files in PROJECT_DIR changed, the timer resets instead of killing the agent.\n\n2. **Null-run detection checks for file modifications** since a pre-run marker created at agent start. If files were modified during the run, the agent is classified as productive regardless of turn count or exit code.\n\n3. **CODER_SUMMARY.md existence** serves as a completion signal — if it was written during the run with 3+ lines, it overrides null-run classification.\n\n**Results:** All 38 tests pass, `shellcheck` clean (only pre-existing SC2034 warnings), `bash -n` passes.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"f0f36cfb-5c7a-484d-9039-d873efba328e","total_cost_usd":2.18496425,"usage":{"input_tokens":39,"cache_creation_input_tokens":84197,"cache_read_input_tokens":2516376,"output_tokens":16014,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":84197,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":39,"outputTokens":16014,"cacheReadInputTokens":2516376,"cacheCreationInputTokens":84197,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":2.18496425,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"b7132064-a594-47d8-b66a-e8